Okay, adding a picture, so.

01:00:39.790 --> 01:00:44.130
Go to the picture icon,
browse to my file, select my file.

01:00:44.210 --> 01:00:48.300
It will upload very,
very quickly to the server.

01:00:48.300 --> 01:00:50.000
