01:02:08.740 --> 01:02:13.650
Well, I can do things like
click on the WWDC tag,

01:02:13.650 --> 01:02:17.500
and I'll get a page of results
that shows me all of the things

01:02:17.500 --> 01:02:19.900
that have been tagged with WWDC.

01:02:19.990 --> 01:02:24.290
If I want to find things that have
been tagged with rumors and WWDC,

01:02:24.420 --> 01:02:28.130
I can filter that down and
look just for those things.

01:02:28.910 --> 01:02:30.760
So it makes it very, very simple.

01:02:30.760 --> 01:02:32.880
Nothing's tender.

01:02:32.880 --> 01:02:34.840
And then up here,
you see a search dialog.

01:02:34.840 --> 01:02:36.460
That does exactly what you would expect.

01:02:36.460 --> 01:02:39.830
It'll search across the entire wiki and
find you all content that contains the

01:02:39.830 --> 01:02:42.500
search term that you've typed in there.

01:02:42.500 --> 01:02:46.620
